The first three films received mixed reviews .
The fourth film received mostly negative reviews .
The fifth film received mixed reviews .
The franchise has been praised for its innovative premise , of the invisible abstract concept of Death killing people , instead of a usual slasher killer ; the death sequences have also been praised for their creativity . !
