CinemaScore FUTURE Section::::Future .
In early 2011 , Tony Todd said in an interview with Dread Central that if Final Destination 5 was a success at the box office , then two sequels would be filmed back - to - back .
On August 23 , 2011 , when asked whether he would be directing a sequel , Steven Quale elaborated , " Who knows .
Never say never .
I mean , it 'll be up to the fans .
We 'll see how this one performs internationally , and if it makes as much money as the fourth one , I 'm sure Warner Brothers will want to make another one . "
